profile: Humane Wildlife Control is Canada's largest urban wildlife removal and exclusion company.  The pioneer in humane wildlife removal for over 20 years. Humane removal and exclusion of raccoons, squirrels, skunks, birds, bats and mice. Accreditied member of the BBB. Humane methods are endorsed by SPCA's across Canada. Guaranteed removal and exclusion. Feces and contaminated insulation removal. Save on energy costs with our energy efficiengt cellulose insulation. Bat Specialists on staff.
